data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value:
This game has 6 rounds and in order to start each one you should press the Start button.
When the round is started Sequencer shows few cards which should be placed below (on the docking stations) in the exact order in which they were presented.
Between each round you can use the earned points to buy helpers from the store. You can use these helpers to reach to the higher rounds much easier.
To reset a card you only need to double click on it.
